    5.0 out of 5 stars Initial impressions very good.
    Reviewed in India on 16 July 2023
    Verified Purchase
    Guys, go for it.
    Great phone with very fast performance. Refresh rate feels so good and then followed by ram management.
    No matter how many apps in the background, it gets loaded in a jiffy.

    Just one suggestion, do not charge the phone at full 120w. Not good in long run. Only do when you have no time.

    Instead choose optimize battery life in settings>optimize battery life. This will charge your phone in around 45 mins but the battery health is greatly preserved.

    Cheers to IQOO for including the charger in the box. As it will cost approx 3k to purchase separately.
